Detailed Description

cvmx_dfa_difrdptr

To write to DFA_DIFRDPTR, a device issues an IOBST request directed at the HFA with addr[34:33] = 0x1. To read DFA_DIFRDPTR, a device issues an IOBLD64 request directed at the HFA with addr[34:33] = 0x1.

If DFA_CONFIG[DTECLKDIS] = 1 (i.e. HFA-HTE clocks are disabled) or if FUSE[90] = 'HFA HTE disable' is blown, read/write operations to DFA_DIFRDPTR do not take effect.
